804
01:22:28,001 --> 01:22:29,253
Lepaskan aku.

805
01:22:32,089 --> 01:22:34,550
Permainan pikiranmu tak akan berhasil untukku.

806
01:22:34,967 --> 01:22:36,176
Victor!

807
01:23:10,419 --> 01:23:12,421
Merasa lebih baik, bukan?

808
01:23:13,630 --> 01:23:15,799
Semua kemarahan itu...

809
01:23:17,009 --> 01:23:18,594
Keluarkan.

810
01:23:18,677 --> 01:23:20,220
Logan!

811
01:23:21,305 --> 01:23:22,431
Kau bukan binatang.

812
01:23:23,474 --> 01:23:25,434
Oh, tentu saja kau binatang.

813
01:23:28,937 --> 01:23:30,147
Lakukan.

814
01:23:34,151 --> 01:23:36,320
Habisi aku.

815
01:24:00,386 --> 01:24:01,178
Logan?

