01:24:29,540 --> 01:24:31,125
Aktifkan Weapon XI.

824
01:24:31,334 --> 01:24:32,377
Prosesnya belum selesai.

825
01:24:32,564 --> 01:24:33,481
Lakukan saja!

826
01:24:33,669 --> 01:24:34,586
Sekarang!

827
01:25:36,273 --> 01:25:37,983
Kau baik-baik saja? Ayolah.

828
01:26:29,847 --> 01:26:31,140
Oke...

829
01:26:32,654 --> 01:26:33,947
Sempurna.

830
01:26:34,239 --> 01:26:35,741
Kayla, bawa mereka keluar.
- Logan...

831
01:26:35,824 --> 01:26:38,160
Cari jalan keluar.

832
01:26:38,243 --> 01:26:40,162
Ayolah, kita pergi!

833
01:26:41,163 --> 01:26:43,165
Wade, apa itu kau?

834
01:26:46,835 --> 01:26:50,047
Kurasa Stryker akhirnya mengetahui cara menutup mulutmu.

835
01:27:00,808 --> 01:27:01,600
Wade...

836
01:27:03,102 --> 01:27:04,645
Kau tak harus melakukan ini.

837
01:27:06,063 --> 01:27:07,314
Atau mungkin kau benar.

838
01:27:22,371 --> 01:27:23,247
Tembak targetnya!

839
