869
01:32:27,552 --> 01:32:28,928
Kita tak ada hubungan lagi.

870
01:32:29,054 --> 01:32:31,514
Kita selalu berhubungan, Jimmy.

871
01:32:31,639 --> 01:32:33,516
Kita bersaudara.

872
01:32:33,600 --> 01:32:36,144
Saudara saling menjaga.

